@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_itsdxi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.52)) - v0)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.30))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.35) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.70)))
    v0 = v2
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.82 * v2 + 0.30) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.35)) / 0.73)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.15 + tmp + 0.07)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
